%========================================================================
% These are some macros I find useful doing e.g. physics textbooks.  
% Some just shorten typing -- it is much easier to
% type \be than \begin{equation}.  Others encapsulate complex commands,
% such as commands that add dynamic links to wikipedia content (which is
